			<div class="content" id="post-content-1210295">
									

<p>It's&#8230; kind of boring. This is somewhat disgusting, but nothing more than that. These aren't really scary at all, and the only danger they pose is decreasing the stability of pipes. They won't even contaminate the water supply, because they wouldn't have anything to eat in pipes that carry purified water. These also seem really hard to contain. The Foundation can't sweep the entire piping system of the world, and some time, some plumber will run into these. Just personal preference, but I'd rather these be protists than worms.</p>

