<p>I love the idea of regurgitating material, and I'll probably try to work that in if that's okay with you VAE. Having someone eaten/crushed would be easy to work in; I was doing some reasearch last night befor I saw your comment Deacon, and I was thinking something like a bird's craw would make more sense too. Another way I could make this creepier would be to up the scale a lot; maybe have a few sewer workers go to investigate a blockage, only to wander in to a gigantic stomach. One of the things I wanted to imply with this article but didn't quite get around to was that this was where dead pets (maybe even people) often ended up, as they get flushed down the toilet or as the worms burrow through the ground (better yet, combine that with regurgitation).</p>
<p>I'll see if I can improve this when I have some spare time.</p>

